Security Operations Fundamentals > [T2]: Lab - Nessus: Features overview

Overview of Nessus and its features.

Nessus comes pre-installed on your lab VM. All you need to do is open up your browser and visit https://127.0.0.1:8834.

Once the console is present, it will prompt for a username and password.

Use the following credentials: 

username: admin 
password: admin

After a successful login, you will get redirected to the Nessus scan console.

Figure - zoom in


Hit the Close button (shown in the screenshot above), proceed to the next page, and click on Create a new scan link.

Figure - zoom in


You will be presented with the scan templates, which is an extensive list of pre-defined templates from Nessus that includes and is not limited to:

  • Malware Scan
  • Mobile Scan
  • Web application Scan
  • Host Discovery
